| `POST /apply-entity-corrections` | No* | Agent tool |
| `POST /generate-spec` | No* | Agent tool |
| `POST /validate-spec` | No | Agent tool |
| `GET /download-bundle-b64` | Yes (header) | HTTP-request node |
| `POST /patch-bundle` | No | HTTP-request node |
| `POST /validate-bundle` | No | Agent tool or HTTP node |
| `POST /upload-bundle` | Yes (header) | HTTP-request node |
| `GET /upload-status/{task_id}` | No | HTTP-request node or Agent tool |

*These endpoints accept conversation_id to look up stored entities, but don't require auth headers per the OpenAPI spec.

